  <details>
    <H1>
      <FONT FACE="Arial, sans-serif">User Cases</FONT>
    </H1>

    <UL>
      <LI>
        <H2>
          <FONT FACE="Arial, sans-serif">Configure Tool</FONT>
        </H2>
      </LI>

      <UL>
        <LI>
          <H2>
            <FONT FACE="Arial, sans-serif">Configure Main Options
            - User is presented with a main configuration
            panel</FONT>
          </H2>
        </LI>

        <OL>
          <LI>
            <P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in">
              <FONT FACE="Arial, sans-serif">Set modules path -
              user enters the path to the modules root
              directory</FONT>
            </P>
          </LI>

          <LI>
            <P>
              <FONT FACE="Arial, sans-serif">Set VulnXML path -
              user enters path to the VulnXML directory</FONT>
            </P>
          </LI>
        </OL>

        <li>
          <H3>
            <FONT FACE="Arial, sans-serif">Configure Spider -
            User is presented with the spider configuration
            panel</FONT>
          </H3>
        </li>

        <OL>
          <LI>
            <P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in">
              <FONT FACE="Arial, sans-serif">Set spider style -
              breadth first or depth first</FONT>
            </P>
          </LI>

          <LI>
            <P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in">
              <FONT FACE="Arial, sans-serif">Set Threads - sets
              no of threads for spider</FONT>
            </P>
          </LI>

          <LI>
            <P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in">
              <FONT FACE="Arial, sans-serif">Set Page Time-outs -
              sets a time-out value</FONT>
            </P>
          </LI>

          <LI>
            <P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in">
              <FONT FACE="Arial, sans-serif">Set 404's - sets
              custom 404 pages the application may use</FONT>
            </P>
          </LI>

          <LI>
            <P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in">
              <FONT FACE="Arial, sans-serif">Set Honor Robot
              Exclusions - Boolean</FONT>
            </P>
          </LI>

          <LI>
            <P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in">
              <FONT FACE="Arial, sans-serif">Set target HTTP
              port</FONT>
            </P>
          </LI>
        </OL>

        <LI>
          <H3>
            <FONT FACE="Arial, sans-serif">Configure Proxy
            Recorder - User is presented with the proxy
            configuration panel</FONT>
          </H3>
        </LI>

        <OL>
          <LI>
            <P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in">
              <FONT FACE="Arial, sans-serif">Set proxy
              port</FONT>
            </P>
          </LI>

          <LI>
            <P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in">
              <FONT FACE="Arial, sans-serif">Start / stop / pause
              proxy ?</FONT>
            </P>
          </LI>

          <LI>
            <P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in">
              <FONT FACE="Arial, sans-serif">Set target HTTP
              port.</FONT>
            </P>
          </LI>
        </OL>

        <LI>
          <H3>
            <FONT FACE="Arial, sans-serif">Configure DataBase -
            User is presented with the database configuration
            panel</FONT>
          </H3>
        </LI>

        <OL>
          <LI>
            <P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in">
              <FONT FACE="Arial, sans-serif">Set db type - User
              sets db type such as Oracle, MySQL etc</FONT>
            </P>
          </LI>

          <LI>
            <P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in">
              <FONT FACE="Arial, sans-serif">Set Connection
              method - user sets connection method such as
              username / password</FONT>
            </P>
          </LI>

          <LI>
            <P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in">
              <FONT FACE="Arial, sans-serif">Test Connection -
              user clicks button to test db connection -
              Boolean</FONT>
            </P>
          </LI>
        </OL>

        <LI>
          <H3>
            <FONT FACE="Arial, sans-serif">Configure Analysis
            Engine</FONT>
          </H3>
        </LI>

        <li>
          <P>
            <FONT FACE="Arial, sans-serif">? Not sure - maybe
            threading only</FONT>
          </P>
        </li>

        <LI>
          <H3>
            <FONT FACE="Arial, sans-serif">Load Modules - User is
            presented with the Modules Main Screen</FONT>
          </H3>
        </LI>

        <OL>
          <LI>
            <P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in">
              <FONT FACE="Arial, sans-serif">Check for new
              modules - user clicks button and checks to see if a
              later modules list file is available</FONT>
            </P>
          </LI>

          <LI>
            <P>
              <FONT FACE="Arial, sans-serif">Load new modules -
              user loads new test modules from local class
              files.</FONT>
            </P>
          </LI>
        </OL>

        <LI>
          <H2>
            <FONT FACE="Arial, sans-serif">Configure Specific
            Module</FONT>
          </H2>
        </LI>

        <OL>
          <LI>
            <P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in">
              <FONT FACE="Arial, sans-serif">Load specific module
              config panel - user selects a specific module
              config</FONT>
            </P>
          </LI>

          <LI>
            <P>
              <FONT FACE="Arial, sans-serif">Sets module config -
              user selects options and saves on exit</FONT>
            </P>
          </LI>
        </OL>

        <LI>
          <H3>
            <FONT FACE="Arial, sans-serif">Load VulnXML</FONT>
          </H3>
        </LI>

        <OL>
          <LI>
            <P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in">
              <FONT FACE="Arial, sans-serif">Check for new files
              - user clicks button and checks if a later file(s)
              is available</FONT>
            </P>
          </LI>

          <LI>
            <P>
              <FONT FACE="Arial, sans-serif">Load new checks -
              user loads new checks from local XML files.</FONT>
            </P>
          </LI>
        </OL>

        <LI>
          <H2>
            <FONT FACE="Arial, sans-serif">Help</FONT>
          </H2>
        </LI>

        <OL>
          <LI>
            <P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in">
              <FONT FACE="Arial, sans-serif">Get version - user
              selects version menu item and is returned the build
              number</FONT>
            </P>
          </LI>

          <LI>
            <P>
              <FONT FACE="Arial, sans-serif">Get API
              Documentation - user selects menu item and tool
              spawns local javadoc in default browser.</FONT>
            </P>
          </LI>
        </OL>
      </UL>
    </UL>

    <UL>
      <LI>
        <H2>
          <FONT FACE="Arial, sans-serif">Analyze Site</FONT>
        </H2>
      </LI>

      <UL>
        <LI>
          <H2>
            <FONT FACE="Arial, sans-serif">New Session</FONT>
          </H2>
        </LI>

        <OL>
          <LI>
            <P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in">
              <FONT FACE="Arial, sans-serif">Create a new session
              - choose a session identifier to group settings and
              results into.</FONT>
            </P>
          </LI>

          <LI>
            <P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in">
              <FONT FACE="Arial, sans-serif">Set application
              discovery location scope - user sets the scope of
              the application discovery. Options would include
              site root, excluded path, not spider outside of
              primary DNS domain, authentication
              credentials.</FONT>
            </P>
          </LI>
        </OL>

        <LI>
          <H2>
            <FONT FACE="Arial, sans-serif">Spider or Proxy
            Recorder</FONT>
          </H2>
        </LI>

        <OL>
          <OL>
            <LI>
              <P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in">
                <FONT FACE="Arial, sans-serif">Spider - start /
                stop and pause spider to crawl the site and
                discover applications that can be tested</FONT>
              </P>
            </LI>

            <UL>
              <LI>
                <P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in">
                  <FONT FACE="Arial, sans-serif">Enters Auth
                  credentials when prompted - if the spider asks
                  the user for auth credentials, the user enters
                  them into a pop-up box and presses
                  continue</FONT>
                </P>
              </LI>

              <LI>
                <P>
                  <FONT FACE="Arial, sans-serif">When prompted
                  for wide scoped form (say form with limitless
                  inputs) user prompted to skip / enter value
                  range or specific values. User enters values
                  and continues.</FONT>
                </P>
              </LI>
            </UL>

            <LI>
              <P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in">
                <FONT FACE="Arial, sans-serif">Start proxy
                recorder - use regular web browser (Internet
                Explorer or Mozilla etc) to browse and interact
                with web applications.</FONT>
              </P>
            </LI>

            <LI>
              <P>
                <FONT FACE="Arial, sans-serif">Stop proxy
                recorder - click button to end proxy recording
                session</FONT>
              </P>
            </LI>
          </OL>
        </OL>

        <LI>
          <H2>
            <FONT FACE="Arial, sans-serif">Generate Security
            Tests</FONT>
          </H2>
        </LI>

        <OL>
          <LI>
            <P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in">
              <FONT FACE="Arial, sans-serif">Generate tests -
              user clicks button to generate the tests for the
              session data from the spider proxy</FONT>
            </P>
          </LI>

          <LI>
            <P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in">
              <FONT FACE="Arial, sans-serif">Validate tests -
              user approves or rejects the proposed tests being
              built</FONT>
            </P>
          </LI>
        </OL>

        <LI>
          <H2>
            <FONT FACE="Arial, sans-serif">Execute Security
            Tests</FONT>
          </H2>
        </LI>

        <OL>
          <LI>
            <P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in">
              <FONT FACE="Arial, sans-serif">Select session -
              user selects session ID tests to execute</FONT>
            </P>
          </LI>

          <LI>
            <P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in">
              <FONT FACE="Arial, sans-serif">Go - User clicks
              button and execute tests</FONT>
            </P>
          </LI>

          <LI>
            <P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in">
              <FONT FACE="Arial, sans-serif">Pause Tests - user
              clicks pause button to pause tests</FONT>
            </P>
          </LI>

          <LI>
            <P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in">
              <FONT FACE="Arial, sans-serif">Stop Tests - User
              clicks button to terminate tests.</FONT>
            </P>
          </LI>
        </OL>

        <LI>
          <H2>
            <FONT FACE="Arial, sans-serif">Generate
            Reports</FONT>
          </H2>
        </LI>
      </UL>
    </UL>

    <OL>
      <LI>
        <P>
          <FONT FACE="Arial, sans-serif">Select Session</FONT>
        </P>
      </LI>

      <LI>
        <P>
          <FONT FACE="Arial, sans-serif">Select report
          type</FONT>
        </P>
      </LI>

      <LI>
        <P>
          <FONT FACE="Arial, sans-serif">Generate report</FONT>
        </P>
      </LI>
    </OL>

